description: Sanctions have been imposed on both sides as a row continues over the presidential election result.
title: Belarus election: Row with EU intensifies over disputed vote
title_page: Belarus election: Row with EU intensifies over disputed vote - BBC News
maintext: A statement from the foreign ministry said: "Belarus is always in words and in fact against confrontation. We are for dialogue and understanding. But as a sovereign state, we are also determined, albeit not without regret, to respond to unfriendly actions in order to naturally protect our national interests."
